<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Seviye 1</title>
<style>
body { background:#0b0b0b; color:#00ff9c; font-family:monospace; text-align:center; padding-top:50px; }
input,button { background:black; color:#00ff9c; border:1px solid #00ff9c; padding:8px; }
.hidden { color:black; }
</style>
